divs: Sighting DetailsWhile I was watching a Bald Eagle glide approximately 20 ft. above me, I felt inspired to take a photo of the street view with the beautiful blue sky. The photo was taken at 3:33pm EDT. At 4:03 - 4:07pm EDT, I took more photos in a different location in Cape Coral that showed the object by the sun, but wasn't visible to the naked eye. After downloading all my photos then reviewing them, I discovered an unknown object in the sky in many photos. The object wasn't seen before, during and after the photos.
